2032
02:06:25,746 --> 02:06:27,338
this is my Jenny.

2033
02:06:27,414 --> 02:06:30,679
Hi. It's nice
to meet you finally.

2034
02:06:40,961 --> 02:06:43,521
Do you, Forrest, take Jenny

2035
