Yes.

2044
02:07:54,535 --> 02:07:56,127
Well, l...

2045
02:07:56,203 --> 02:07:58,330
I don't know.

2046
02:07:58,405 --> 02:08:00,464
<i>Sometimes it would stop raining</i>

2047
02:08:00,541 --> 02:08:03,942
<i>long enough for</i>
<i>the stars to come out...</i>

2048
02:08:06,880 --> 02:08:08,814
<i>and then it was nice.</i>

2049
02:08:12,086 --> 02:08:15,146
It was like just
before the sun goes to bed

2050
02:08:15,222 --> 02:08:16,621
